These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: d&b, house, jazz, blues
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, librarian, pilot, videographer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, mystery, time-travel, zombie
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, apricot, ivory, amber
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, video-games, collecting, cooking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, cycling, handball, parkour
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, orchid, dahlia, bellflower
 1. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
 2. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's hobby is baking##1
 3. the fan of jazz is not the person who growsorchid##6
 4. the person who growsdahlia is not the fan of house##6
 5. the person who likes amber is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
 6. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
 7. the person who growsbellflower is not the person who's sport is cycling##6
 8. the person who likes ebony is the coach##1
 9. the pilot is not the fan of blues##6
10. the videographer is the person who growsorchid##1
11. the pilot is the person who growsazalea##1
12. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far right##1
13. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
14. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere to the right of the librarian##5
15. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
16. the person who growsdahlia is somewhere between the person who growsorchid and the person who growsbellflower##7
17. the person who's sport is parkour is not the person who likes ebony##6
18. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the fan of blues##1
19. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere between the coach and the person who's sport is baseball##7
20. the person who's hobby is video-games is not the fan of blues##6
21. the videographer is somewhere to the left of the pilot##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre          | d&b      | blues   | house     | jazz |
| Job           | videographer | librarian   | coach    | pilot     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie       | time-travel | horror   | mystery   |
| Color   | ivory      | amber     | ebony | apricot    |
| Hobby           | video-games   | cooking       | collecting  | baking       |
| Sport         | baseball     | cycling     | handball | parkour   |
| Flower     | orchid          | dahlia      | bellflower     | azalea      |

