 9. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
10. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the left of the cape-cod house##5
11. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the right of the malaysian##5
12. the colonial house is on the far right##1
13. the person playing domino is somewhere to the left of the person who likes brown##5
14. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person who likes red##1
15. the person playing domino is in an odd position##4
16. the person who likes apricot is in an odd position##4
17. the person playing billiard is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
18. the person eating cabbage is somewhere to the right of the person eating carrot##5
19. the french is somewhere between the person playing domino and the owner of the hedgehog##7
20. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3
21. the person driving the van is on the far left##1
22. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the colonial house##5
23. the french is not the art-deco house##6
24. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person playing chess and the indian##2

